Congratulations! You've found your dream partner. However, they have one...interesting trait. Do you Make or Break it?

Play with friends at parties, or play with your significant other to learn more about each other!

OVER 100 Funny and Interesting Traits! 
(All traits are safe for work)

Warning: friendships may be questioned after playing this game.
